let mySentence = "Welcome here, Everyone!"
let findWord = /everyone/i;    //<- this is the code

let result = findWord.test(mySentence);

//the result 
//=============================
true
//=============================


/*
I can match the string that i want to find by ignoring the Case. It can happend by adding the flag.
The flag that can be used to ignore the Case is "i".
By adding this flag, I can get the true result by ignoring the Letter Case (uppercase, lowercase,)
*/
